"p",{},"Node 预设是 Nuxt 的默认预设，构建项目时，Nuxt 会输出一个 Node.js 服务器，你可以通过 ",[235,236,237],"code",{},"node .output/server/index.mjs"," 来运行它。",[226,240,241],{"id":241},"环境要求",[231,243,244,245,248],{},"如果你使用默认的 ",[235,246,247],{},"better-sqlite3"," 模块来操作 sqlite 数据库，则必须部署在 Glibc 版本高于 2.29 的操作系统上，例如 Debian 11、Ubuntu 20.04。",[250,251,252],"note",{},[231,253,254,255,258,259,266],{},"你可以使用 ",[235,256,257],{},"ldd --version"," 检查 Glibc 版本。更多信息请参见 ",[260,261,265],"a",{"href":262,"rel":263},"https://github.com/nuxt/content/issues/3248",[264],"nofollow","issue #3248","。",[226,268,270],{"id":269},"使用-nodejs-预设构建","使用 Node.js 预设构建",[231,272,273],{},"使用 Nuxt 构建命令构建项目：",[275,276,282],"pre",{"className":277,"code":278,"filename":279,"language":280,"meta":281,"style":281},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter material-theme material-theme-palenight","nuxi build\n","Terminal","bash","",[235,283,284],{"__ignoreMap":281},[285,286,289,293],"span",{"class":287,"line":288},"line",1,[285,290,292],{"class":291},"sBMFI","nuxi",[285,294,296],{"class":295},"sfazB"," build\n",[231,298,299,300,303],{},"使用 Node 服务器预设运行 ",[235,301,302],{},"nuxi build"," 后，结果将是一个启动可运行 Node 服务器的入口点。",[275,305,307],{"className":277,"code":306,"filename":279,"language":280,"meta":281,"style":281},"$ node .output/server/index.mjs\nListening on http://localhost:3000\n",[235,308,309,320],{"__ignoreMap":281},[285,310,311,314,317],{"class":287,"line":288},[285,312,313],{"class":291},"$",[285,315,316],{"class":295}," node",[285,318,319],{"class":295}," .output/server/index.mjs\n",[285,321,323,326,329],{"class":287,"line":322},2,[285,324,325],{"class":291},"Listening",[285,327,328],{"class":295}," on",[285,330,331],{"class":295}," http://localhost:3000\n",[250,333,334],{},[231,335,336],{},"SQLite 数据库将在服务器启动时在服务器端加载，同时在浏览器中用于客户端导航或操作。",[338,339,340],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sBMFI, html code.shiki .sBMFI{--shiki-light:#E2931D;--shiki-default:#FFCB6B;--shiki-dark:#FFCB6B}html pre.shiki code .sfazB, html code.shik